        but there is still much room for improvement in the accuracy of small object
        detection. This research aims to improve the detection accuracy of small
        objects by examining what processing is important for improving accuracy.
        Based on the results of this examination, we propose a new method to improve
        the accuracy of small object detection.
      </div>
